# FLASK :: file upload demo
Demo project powered by Flask about file upload via HTTP request

## Prerequisites
Install [Flask](http://flask.pocoo.org/) via virtualenv
```
$ pip install virtualenv
$ virtualenv flask
```
Install local dependencies
```
$ flask/bin/pip install flask
$ flask/bin/pip install flask-cors
```

## Installing
Install npm packages
```
$ npm install
```
Change file permission for app.py
```
$ chmod a+x app.py
```

## How to run
1. Run Flask API server
```
$ ./app.py
```
2. Run web client (http-server)
```
$ npm start
```

